Users of this dataset must credit this derived dataset as well as the original data sources listed below.

This project uses and extends open data from:

- City of Vienna / Stadt Wien. (2025). Donauinsel Freizeiteinrichtungen Standorte Wien [Data set]. data.gv.at.  
  https://www.data.gv.at/datasets/4e8d237b-8bd4-4483-a85d-431784c543b9?locale=de  
  Attribution: “Stadt Wien - data.wien.gv.at”  


- ÖVDAT. (2026). GIP / Graphenintegrations-Plattform Österreich [Data set]. data.gv.at.  
  https://www.data.gv.at/katalog/dataset/3fefc838-791d-4dde-975b-a4131a54e7c5  
  Attribution: “ÖVDAT/GIP.at - Graphenintegrations-Plattform Österreich”

Changes were made to the original data. The dataset was enriched with field-collected observations, additional attributes, photos, and spatial analysis results.

